text: Kiril "Kiro" Dojčinovski (Macedonian: Kиpил Kиpo Дojчинoвcки; 17 October 1943 – 10 August 2022) was a Macedonian footballer. He played for the Yugoslavia national football team from 1968 until 1970, making six appearances. Dojčinovski died on 10 August 2022 at the age of 78. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Yugoslavian footballers
